        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/parker-solar-probe-artists-concept.png" alt="An artist's concept showing Parker Solar Probe" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
         <mj-text padding="0px 12px 4px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;"><i>An artist's concept showing Parker Solar Probe. Credits: NASA/APL
</i></p>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              border-left: 3px solid #4D3060;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
                    "><strong>NASA's Parker Solar Probe recently completed its 23rd close encounter with the Sun</strong>, <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-24-03-2025-br6-9-matching-its-previous-records" target="_blank">matching its previous records</a> for speed and proximity. The spacecraft reached a distance of 3.8 Mn miles from the solar surface and achieved a speed of 430,000 mph while collecting valuable data from within the Sun’s corona.</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              border-left: 3px solid #4D3060;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
                    "><strong>AstroForge, a start-up, aims to mine valuable metals from asteroids, starting with its spacecraft Odin</strong>. Despite communication issues, the company plans to continue its mission to extract metals like platinum. There are concerns about the feasibility, environmental impact, and legal ownership of space resources (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-24-03-2025-br7-10-more-about-space-mining" target="_blank">more about space mining</a>).</p>
                  
                    
        </mj-text>
